stories.title: Ask HN: Does anyone else see app installs fall after the Playstore redesign?

stories.text:
I just googled "apple pages move graphical element to same location on each page" and got a bunch of apple support pages, for example https://support.apple.com/en-au/guide/pages/tanc9ead56b9/mac which gave me

We're sorry.

We can't find the page you're looking for.

so I tried to do a different non related query "apple ios fix settings" and got the same experience under an en-ng path

however experimenting a bit showed me that at least some Apple support pages were available not under the en language codes.

Not to important, just amusing.
